text: The SWAPO Party Youth League (SPYL), formerly SWAPO Youth League (SYL), is the youth wing of the SWAPO Party, the ruling party of Namibia.Swapo party constitution It shares the same principles as those of the SWAPO Party.Nathanael Keshii, 2017: A Journey to Exile: The Story of a Namibian Freedom Fighter, == References == Category:1969 establishments in Africa Category:20th-century establishments in Namibia Category:Political parties in Namibia Category:Windhoek
title: SWAPO Party Youth League
